query:
SELECT uc.user_id, u.peertube_account_id, uc.is_admin, um.key_value AS public_name
            FROM user_club uc
            JOIN user_meta um ON uc.user_id = um.user_id
            JOIN users u ON uc.user_id = u.id
            WHERE uc.club_id = $1
                AND um.key_name = 's:publicName'
            ORDER BY um.user_id
            LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3
